::Shadow Wing::

She looked at Stegotron.
"Maybe you could talk to him. Male to male.  If his prides the 
question, he might respond better you than he would me. Please go and 
try to reason with him."
She looked a little blue.  She knew that this was hard on Lunarpine 
and harder on her. She smiled and said with sarcasm, "Oh, and when 
you find him, tell that flea bag that I shall see him for sparring 
tomorrow."  She smiled at Stegotron.  She thought, even if he 
repeated that to him word for word, he'll be good and riled tomorrow. 
She chuckled to herself.
